From 1bf568bddf99337573b97378c17bc29a9c5fff93 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Jan Moeller <Jan.Moeller@governikus.de>
Date: Mon, 15 Sep 2025 13:31:26 +0200
Subject: a11y: Consider modal property of QML PopupItem in QAccessible::State

Introduce QAccessibleQuickPopupItem to allow access to the a11y properties
of the QML Popup. This uses the QQuickPopupItem as QQuickPopup does not
derive from QQuickItem and the popup item is the actual parent of the
popup's content.

Task-number: QTBUG-140200
Pick-to: 6.11
Change-Id: Id4a89894bc0576410b8a184dd6f18bfb1c8b2b8f
Reviewed-by: Michael Weghorn <m.weghorn@posteo.de>
(cherry picked from commit bfa68afb5a62b8cf09f5f5a478bbc0d0b805cc85)
---
